data.description: **$4,000 incentive for buyers to lower interest rate or repairs with the right offer. Repair update: Wall removed in garage and fully usable for parking.** Welcome to 841 Satellite View, located in the heart of Texas. This beautiful home is equipped with solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency and cost savings. With ample storage space, you'll have plenty of room for all your belongings. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow and an abundance of natural light. Perfectly situated, this property is conveniently close to a golf course, shopping centers, and a variety of restaurants. Families will appreciate the proximity to Caldwell Elementary School, which happens to be just across the street. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home in Texas.
